*<div id="domcharacterdata.substringdata" class="refentry">  <div class="refnamediv">   <h1 class="refname">DOMCharacterData::substringData</h1>   <p class="verinfo">(PHP 5, PHP 7)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">DOMCharacterData::substringData</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">    Extracts a range of data from the node   </span></p>   </div>  <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-domcharacterdata.substringdata-description">   <h3 class="title">说明</h3>   <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description" style="border:1px gray;padding-left:5px;background:#232525">    <span class="modifier">public</span> <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">string</span> <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>DOMCharacterData::substringData</strong></span>     ( <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$offset</span></span>    , <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$count</span></span>    )</div>    <p class="para rdfs-comment">    Returns the specified substring.    </p>  </div>   <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-domcharacterdata.substringdata-parameters">   <h3 class="title">参数</h3>   <span>    <dl>            <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">offset</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        Start offset of substring to extract.       </p>      </dd>                 <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">count</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        The number of characters to extract.       </p>      </dd>          </dl>    </span>  </div>   <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class